ford 2014)\n*[[200 metres]] \u2013 20.76 (+1.1&nbsp;m/s, Loughborough 2013)\n'''Indoor'''\n*[[60 metres]] \u2013 6.54 (Sheffield 2016)\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{iaaf name|238732}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Robertson, Andrew}}\n[[Category:1990 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Grantham]]\n[[Category:English male sprinters]]\n[[Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for England]]\n[[Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in athletics]]\n[[Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2014 Commonwealth Games]]\n[[Category:World Athletics Championships athletes for Great Britain]]\n[[Category:Commonwealth Games silver medallists for England]]\n{{UK-athletics-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|British athlete}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2018}}\n{{Infobox athlete\n| name           = Andrew Robertson\n| image          = Andy Robertson 2015.jpg\n| caption        = Andy Robertson in 2015\n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1990|12|17|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = [[Grantham]], England\n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| height         = 1.75 m<ref>[http://g2014results.thecgf.com/athlete/athletics/1033086/a_robertson.html 2014 CWG bio]</ref>\n| weight         = 69 kg\n| sport          = [[Athletics (sport)|Athletics]]\n| event          = [[60 m]], [[100 m]], [[200 m]]\n| club           = Sale Harriers<ref name=\"P10\">[http://www.thepowerof10.info/athletes/profile.aspx?athleteid=21361 Power of 10 profile]</ref>\n| collegeteam    = \n| education      = \n| coach          = Sam Robertson<ref name=\"P10\"/>\n| medaltemplates = {{Medal|Sport | Men's Athletics}}\n{{Medal|Country|{{ENG}}}}\n{{Medal|Competition|[[Commonwealth Games]]}}\n{{Medal|Silver|[[2014 Commonwealth Games|2014 Glasgow]]|[[Athletics at the 2014 Commonwealth Games \u2013 Men's 4 \u00d7 100 metres relay|4x100 m relay]]}}\n}}\n\n'''Andrew Robertson''' (born 17 December 1990) is an English [[s